    "In the process of max pooling, only the maximum value within a small window or region is selected as a representative, while discarding other detailed information.",
    "This operation leads to partial information loss in the original data and reduces the accuracy of features.",
    "The mathematical expression of this method is shown as Eq.",
    "where x is the values of the input image in the pooling region.",
    "The 2 × 2 matrix obtained when a maximum pooling of 3 × 3 filter size is applied on a 6x6 pixel is shown in Figure 3."
